reviewText: This show is a dark comedy about day-to-day life.  I like shows that require me to pay attention and there are a lot of little things that happen, glances, expressions that are missed if you don't pay attention.
Why is this, in the description, called Liverpudlian? It's based in Manchester, not Liverpool. It's Mancunian! Brilliant too, one of the best!
Want to watch a group of people sitting in their "lounge", smoking, farting, and talking about the most inane topics? Then this is for you.
